.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-SPENDABLE-BALANCE-VARIANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-spendable-balance-variance \- FEAT-3650 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-spendable-balance-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the variance of spendable balances in msat across all peer channels (FEAT-3650).
.PP
Output: JSON with key spendable_balance_variance_msat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
